               <msContents class="#STM">
                  <summary><p>A copy of the <title xml:lang="ta">Tiruvātavūrar Purāṇam</title>, entitled here <title xml:lang="ta">Vātavūrappurāṇam</title>, that is, a poem on the life of <persName>Māṇikkavācakar</persName>, by <persName role="author">Kaṭavuṇmāmuṉivar</persName> (15th century?). See Sweetman &amp; Ilakkuvan (2012, p. 66), Zvelebil (1995, p. 334, 405).</p>
<p>Wrongly identified as <title xml:lang="ta">Nālu Mantirik Katai</title>, as the first intertitle (<title xml:lang="ta">Mantiriccarukkam</title>) was taken as the title.</p>

<p>Description based on the examination of the original manuscript (February 2023).</p>
<p>Dimensions assessed at the time of examination.</p>     </summary>
                  
